What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Radiotherapy Market?

Market Analysis and Size

The global incidence of cancer was on the rise, and radiotherapy is a crucial treatment modality for many cancer types. As the population continues to age and lifestyles change, the number of cancer cases was expected to increase, driving demand for radiotherapy. Increased awareness about cancer and its treatment options, along with improved screening and early detection methods, led to more individuals seeking cancer treatments, including radiotherapy. In many countries, healthcare spending has been increasing, providing more funding for advanced treatments like radiotherapy. Governments and private healthcare providers have been investing in upgrading their facilities and equipment.

